invalid type: string "Company Policy & Pricing Data\n1. Refund Policy\nRefunds are allowed within 30 days for bulk orders.\nExceptions apply for custom products or services.\nAll refund requests must be submitted in writing.\n2. Product Pricing\nProduct       Price       Date\nWidget A      $100        2025-03-01\nWidget B      $200        2025-03-05\nWidget C      $150        2025-03-10\n team,\n